xt-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12);\">2012.11-2013.04，吉利汽车研究院，资深专家（副总级）</span></p><p style=\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12);\">2011.06-2013.04，吉利汽车研究院，院长助理（副总级），分管产品战略及策划、知识产权管理、商务管理等业务；协助研究院运营与管理</span></p><p style=\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12);\">2010.06-2011.06，吉利汽车研究院，产品战略及策划部，部长</span></p><p style=\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12);\">2009.09-2010.06，吉利汽车研究院，项目管理部，一级高级项目经理</span></p><p style=\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12);\">2008.09-2009.09，吉利汽车研究院，技术管理部，副部长</span></p><p style=\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(12, 12, 12);\">2007.07-2008.09，浙江吉利控股集团，集团技术部，专业经理</span></p><p><br></p></div><div class=\"center-div tli-content yj-part tli-content-\"><p style=\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 10.5pt; font-family: 宋体;\">主要从事技术路线评价与决策、技术创新体系建设及汽车产业发展战略等研究</span><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"></span></span></p><p><br></p></div><div class=\"center-div tli-content xs-job tli-content-\"><p style=\";text-align:justify;text-justify:inter-ideograph\"><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;; font-size: 14px;\"></span></p><p style=\";font-size: 16px;font-family: 宋体;white-space: normal;text-align: justify\"><spa